CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 28 reads: " Free Prizes, Samples and Demonstrations Galore...10. Miss Joanne Neal and Robert Ficklin represented the Pitt Storm Window Company and passed out literature...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Robert Ficklin and Joanne Neal gathered in Pitt Storm Window Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
